OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779289870
OL,3,CThames Water should be allowed to
OL,4,C'collapse and start again', Oxford MP
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe Oxford West and Abingdon MP was
OL,8,Fresponding to claims in The Guardian
OL,9,Fthat a takeover deal had run into
OL,10,Fproblems because of the uncertainty
OL,11,Fsurrounding Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Fposition in Downing Street.
OL,14,F"This rescue deal just delays the
OL,15,Finevitable. What we want to see from
OL,16,Fthe government is to take seriously
OL,17,Fthe plans the Liberal Democrats have
OL,18,Fput forward to make this a public
OL,19,Fservice company," Ms Moran told ITV
OL,20,FNews Meridian.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@QO]
