OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779289870
OL,3,CThames Water should be allowed to
OL,4,C'collapse and start again', Oxford MP
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"This is a company that is too large,
OL,8,Ftoo cumbersome, not viable enough. It
OL,9,Fneeds total restructuring. Actually,
OL,10,Fthe best thing in its own interests,
OL,11,Flet alone the interests of taxpayers,
OL,12,Fis to let it collapse and start again."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the company said:
OL,15,F"Thames Water is working to secure a
OL,16,Fstable, long-term future for the
OL,17,Fbusiness, support continued
OL,18,Fimprovements for customers and the
OL,19,Fenvironment, and progress with its
OL,20,Foperational turnaround plan."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@gO]wD@AOU|D@]O]
