OL,3,CThames Water should be allowed to
OL,4,C'collapse and start again', Oxford MP
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe Department for the Environment,
OL,8,FFood and Rural Affairs said in a
OL,9,Fstatement: "The Government will always
OL,10,Fact in the national interest on these
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"The company remains financially
OL,14,Fstable, but we stand ready for all
OL,15,Feventualities, including applying for
OL,16,Fa Special Administration Regime if
OL,17,Fthat were to become necessary."
OL,26,@qD@LOUuD@AOUyD@_O]
